cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.MM, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with real-time video classification systems and perturbations on images. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the brittleness of machine learning systems to adversarial perturbations. 
3. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is another likely category as the paper deals with generating adversarial examples that can cause misclassification in surveillance applications. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with video classification systems. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the use of generative adversarial network (GAN) architectures to generate adversarial samples.
